These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: brazilian, turkish
1. Nationality:brazilian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Nationality   | turkish | brazilian |

 #################################
 
